{
  "uid": "nuc-overview",
  "title": "NUC System Overview",
  "tags": ["infrastructure", "nuc"],
  "timezone": "Europe/Dublin",
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 4,

  "panels": [

    { "collapsed": false, "gridPos": {"h":1,"w":24,"x":0,"y":0}, "id":100, "title":"⚡ System Health at a Glance", "type":"row" },

    {
      "id": 1, "title": "CPU %",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {"h":5,"w":4,"x":0,"y":1},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"100 - (avg(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[2m])) * 100)","legendFormat":"CPU %","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"percent","min":0,"max":100,"thresholds":{"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"green","value":0},{"color":"yellow","value":60},{"color":"red","value":85}]}}}
    },

    {
      "id": 2, "title": "CPU Temp (°C)",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {"h":5,"w":4,"x":4,"y":1},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"max(node_hwmon_temp_celsius{chip=\"platform_coretemp_0\"})","legendFormat":"Package °C","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"celsius","min":20,"max":90,"thresholds":{"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"green","value":0},{"color":"yellow","value":65},{"color":"red","value":80}]}}}
    },

    {
      "id": 3, "title": "RAM Used / Total",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h":5,"w":4,"x":8,"y":1},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr":"(node_memory_MemTotal_bytes - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes) / 1024/1024/1024","legendFormat":"Used GB","refId":"A","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}},
        {"expr":"node_memory_MemTotal_bytes / 1024/1024/1024","legendFormat":"Total GB","refId":"B","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"decgbytes","decimals":1}}
    },

    {
      "id": 4, "title": "Disk Used %",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {"h":5,"w":4,"x":12,"y":1},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"100 - ((node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint=\"/\",fstype!=\"rootfs\"} / node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint=\"/\",fstype!=\"rootfs\"}) * 100)","legendFormat":"Disk %","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"percent","min":0,"max":100,"thresholds":{"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"green","value":0},{"color":"yellow","value":70},{"color":"red","value":85}]}}}
    },

    {
      "id": 5, "title": "Disk Free",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h":5,"w":4,"x":16,"y":1},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint=\"/\",fstype!=\"rootfs\"} / 1024/1024/1024","legendFormat":"Free GB","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"decgbytes","decimals":1}}
    },

    {
      "id": 6, "title": "Total Docker RAM",
      "type": "stat",
      "description": "All 9 Docker containers combined. n8n is the largest at ~320 MB.",
      "gridPos": {"h":5,"w":4,"x":20,"y":1},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"sum(docker_container_memory_bytes{name=~\"sparc-.+|gardening-.+\"}) / 1024/1024","legendFormat":"Docker MB","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"decmbytes","decimals":0,"thresholds":{"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"green","value":0},{"color":"yellow","value":900},{"color":"red","value":1200}]}}}
    },

    { "collapsed": false, "gridPos": {"h":1,"w":24,"x":0,"y":6}, "id":101, "title":"📊 CPU & RAM Trend", "type":"row" },

    {
      "id": 10, "title": "CPU Usage % (trend)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h":8,"w":12,"x":0,"y":7},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"100 - (avg(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[2m])) * 100)","legendFormat":"CPU %","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"percent","min":0,"max":100,"color":{"fixedColor":"blue","mode":"fixed"},"custom":{"fillOpacity":15}}}
    },

    {
      "id": 11, "title": "RAM Breakdown (GB)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h":8,"w":12,"x":12,"y":7},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr":"(node_memory_MemTotal_bytes - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes) / 1024/1024/1024","legendFormat":"Used","refId":"A","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}},
        {"expr":"node_memory_Cached_bytes / 1024/1024/1024","legendFormat":"Cached","refId":"B","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}},
        {"expr":"node_memory_MemFree_bytes / 1024/1024/1024","legendFormat":"Free","refId":"C","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit":"decgbytes"},
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher":{"id":"byName","options":"Used"},  "properties":[{"id":"color","value":{"fixedColor":"red","mode":"fixed"}}]},
          {"matcher":{"id":"byName","options":"Cached"},"properties":[{"id":"color","value":{"fixedColor":"yellow","mode":"fixed"}}]},
          {"matcher":{"id":"byName","options":"Free"},  "properties":[{"id":"color","value":{"fixedColor":"green","mode":"fixed"}}]}
        ]
      }
    },

    { "collapsed": false, "gridPos": {"h":1,"w":24,"x":0,"y":15}, "id":102, "title":"🐳 Container Memory & CPU", "type":"row" },

    {
      "id": 20, "title": "Container RAM (MB) — sorted by usage",
      "description": "docker stats refreshed every 30s via cron → node_exporter textfile. n8n is the largest consumer.",
      "type": "bargauge",
      "gridPos": {"h":9,"w":14,"x":0,"y":16},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"sort_desc(docker_container_memory_bytes{name=~\"sparc-.+|gardening-.+\"} / 1024/1024)","legendFormat":"{{name}}","instant":true,"datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions":{"calcs":["lastNotNull"]},"orientation":"horizontal","displayMode":"gradient","minVizHeight":15},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"decmbytes","thresholds":{"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"green","value":0},{"color":"yellow","value":200},{"color":"red","value":400}]}}}
    },

    {
      "id": 21, "title": "Container CPU % (current)",
      "type": "bargauge",
      "gridPos": {"h":9,"w":10,"x":14,"y":16},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"sort_desc(docker_container_cpu_percent{name=~\"sparc-.+|gardening-.+\"})","legendFormat":"{{name}}","instant":true,"datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions":{"calcs":["lastNotNull"]},"orientation":"horizontal","displayMode":"gradient","minVizHeight":15},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"percent","thresholds":{"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"green","value":0},{"color":"yellow","value":10},{"color":"red","value":30}]}}}
    },

    {
      "id": 22, "title": "Container RAM trend (MB)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h":8,"w":24,"x":0,"y":25},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"docker_container_memory_bytes{name=~\"sparc-.+|gardening-.+\"} / 1024/1024","legendFormat":"{{name}}","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"decmbytes"}},
      "options": {"legend":{"calcs":["lastNotNull","max"],"displayMode":"table","placement":"right"}}
    },

    { "collapsed": false, "gridPos": {"h":1,"w":24,"x":0,"y":33}, "id":103, "title":"🟢 Container Status", "type":"row" },

    {
      "id": 30, "title": "Container Running Status",
      "description": "1 = running (refreshed every 30s). Any container showing 0 or missing needs investigation.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h":6,"w":24,"x":0,"y":34},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"docker_container_running{name=~\"sparc-.+|gardening-.+\"}","legendFormat":"{{name}}","instant":true,"datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs":["lastNotNull"]},
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "orientation": "horizontal"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [{"type":"value","options":{"1":{"text":"🟢 UP","color":"green"},"0":{"text":"🔴 DOWN","color":"red"}}}],
          "thresholds": {"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"red","value":null},{"color":"green","value":1}]}
        }
      }
    },

    { "collapsed": false, "gridPos": {"h":1,"w":24,"x":0,"y":40}, "id":104, "title":"🌡️ Temperature & Network", "type":"row" },

    {
      "id": 40, "title": "CPU Temperature (°C)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h":8,"w":12,"x":0,"y":41},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr":"max(node_hwmon_temp_celsius{chip=\"platform_coretemp_0\"})","legendFormat":"Package (max)","refId":"A","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}},
        {"expr":"node_hwmon_temp_celsius{chip=\"platform_coretemp_0\",sensor=\"temp2\"}","legendFormat":"Core 0","refId":"B","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}},
        {"expr":"node_hwmon_temp_celsius{chip=\"platform_coretemp_0\",sensor=\"temp3\"}","legendFormat":"Core 1","refId":"C","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit":"celsius","min":20,"max":90},
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher":{"id":"byName","options":"Package (max)"},"properties":[{"id":"color","value":{"fixedColor":"orange","mode":"fixed"}},{"id":"custom.lineWidth","value":2}]}
        ]
      },
      "options": {"legend":{"calcs":["lastNotNull","max"],"displayMode":"table","placement":"bottom"}}
    },

    {
      "id": 41, "title": "Network In/Out (KB/s)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h":8,"w":12,"x":12,"y":41},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr":"rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{device=\"wlp2s0\"}[2m]) / 1024","legendFormat":"RX KB/s","refId":"A","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}},
        {"expr":"rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{device=\"wlp2s0\"}[2m]) / 1024","legendFormat":"TX KB/s","refId":"B","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit":"KBs"},
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher":{"id":"byName","options":"RX KB/s"},"properties":[{"id":"color","value":{"fixedColor":"green","mode":"fixed"}}]},
          {"matcher":{"id":"byName","options":"TX KB/s"},"properties":[{"id":"color","value":{"fixedColor":"blue","mode":"fixed"}}]}
        ]
      }
    },

    { "collapsed": false, "gridPos": {"h":1,"w":24,"x":0,"y":49}, "id":105, "title":"💾 Disk I/O", "type":"row" },

    {
      "id": 50, "title": "Disk Read/Write throughput (KB/s)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h":8,"w":12,"x":0,"y":50},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr":"rate(node_disk_read_bytes_total{device=\"sda\"}[2m]) / 1024","legendFormat":"Read KB/s","refId":"A","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}},
        {"expr":"rate(node_disk_written_bytes_total{device=\"sda\"}[2m]) / 1024","legendFormat":"Write KB/s","refId":"B","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit":"KBs"},
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher":{"id":"byName","options":"Read KB/s"}, "properties":[{"id":"color","value":{"fixedColor":"green","mode":"fixed"}}]},
          {"matcher":{"id":"byName","options":"Write KB/s"},"properties":[{"id":"color","value":{"fixedColor":"orange","mode":"fixed"}}]}
        ]
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 51, "title": "Disk I/O Utilisation %",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h":8,"w":12,"x":12,"y":50},
      "datasource": {"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr":"rate(node_disk_io_time_seconds_total{device=\"sda\"}[2m]) * 100","legendFormat":"IO util %","datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"sparc-prometheus"}}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults":{"unit":"percent","min":0,"max":100,"thresholds":{"mode":"absolute","steps":[{"color":"green","value":0},{"color":"yellow","value":40},{"color":"red","value":75}]}}}
    },

    { "collapsed": false, "gridPos": {"h":1,"w":24,"x":0,"y":58}, "id":106, "title":"🗄️ Technology Stack", "type":"row" },

    {
      "id": 60, "title": "Service Stack",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"h":6,"w":24,"x":0,"y":59},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## ⚡ Sparc Energy Stack\n| Service | Technology | Notes |\n|---------|-----------|-------|\n| **Primary Database** | **TimescaleDB** (PostgreSQL 16) | Time-series hypertables + full SQL. Container: `sparc-db` |\n| **Cache** | Redis 7 | AOF persistence · 256 MB cap · allkeys-lru eviction |\n| **API** | FastAPI + LightGBM | H+24 load forecast · ControlEngine · Solar Advisory |\n| **Automation** | n8n 2.19 | 5 active workflows (Alert Relay, Morning Brief, Drift Check). Shared with 🌱 Gardening. |\n| **Reverse Proxy** | Caddy 2 | Auto-TLS · HTTP/3 |\n\n## 🌱 Gardening Stack\n| Service | Technology | Notes |\n|---------|-----------|-------|\n| **Time-series DB** | InfluxDB 2.7 | Sensor streams: soil, temp, humidity, LVPD. Container: `gardening-influxdb` |\n| **Visualisation** | Grafana OSS 11 | 25-panel dashboard · http://localhost:3000. Container: `gardening-grafana` |\n| **Hub** | Streamlit | Live LVPD · GDD · harvest log · RAG. Container: `gardening-streamlit` |\n| **Poller** | Python Ecowitt API | 5 min poll → InfluxDB. Container: `gardening-poller` |\n\n## 🔧 Shared Infrastructure\n| Service | Technology | Notes |\n|---------|-----------|-------|\n| **Monitoring** | Prometheus v2.52 → Grafana OSS 11 | Scrapes node_exporter + textfile collector (cAdvisor workaround) |\n| **Container UI** | Portainer CE | Full Docker management · http://localhost:9000 |\n\n> **ADR-012:** Sparc uses TimescaleDB (UPDATE/FK on `recommendations`, `households` — impossible in InfluxDB). Gardening uses InfluxDB (pure append-only sensor streams). See `docs/adr/ADR-012`."
      }
    }

  ]
}
